    %% Product Components
    STEP1B[1b. WooCommerce product components]
    STEP1B --> PRODUCT_NAME[ProductName - product name with link]
    STEP1B --> PRODUCT_TYPE[ProductType - product type tag with icons]
    STEP1B --> PRODUCT_PRICE[ProductPrice - formatted price display]
    STEP1B --> PRODUCT_TOTAL_SALES[ProductTotalSales - sales count]
    STEP1B --> PRODUCT_CAT[ProductCat - category tags]
    STEP1B --> PRODUCT_STOCK[ProductStock - stock status display]
    STEP1B --> PRODUCT_BOUND[ProductBoundItems - bound items list]

    %% User Components
    STEP1C[1c. WordPress user components]
    STEP1C --> USER_NAME[UserName - user display with avatar]
    STEP1C --> USER_AVATAR[UserAvatarUpload - avatar uploader]
    STEP1C --> USER_FILTER[UserFilter - user search and filter form]
    STEP1C --> USER_ROLE[UserRole - role tag display]

